Of course
You don't need the old phone, you can use a new one. All you need to do is receive an SMS code in order to register your number.

```php
$username = "your phone number including country code";
$token = md5($username);
$nickname = "Derp";
$w = new WhatsProt($username, $token, $nickname, true);
$w->requestCode();
```
this should get you an SMS code
now use
```php
$username = "your phone number including country code";
$token = md5($username);
$nickname = "Derp";
$w = new WhatsProt($username, $token, $nickname, true);
$result = $w->registerCode("6-digit SMS code you received");
$password = $result->pw;
echo "Password is $password";
```
this should return your password

now you can use
```php
$username = "your phone number including country code";
$token = md5($username);
$nickname = "Derp";
$password = "password you received";// e.g. "SDFStsdgDFHDFGSDgfsd==";
$w = new WhatsProt($username, $token, $nickname, true);
$w->Connect();
$w->LoginWithPassword($password);

send messages etc.
```

